{
    "version": 4,
    "bundle": "Q62CG3V4LK77FKCGRJRWKZ4VNJ2QCP44",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801059001",
    "title": "やってみてもいい",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレーナーとして校内新聞の取材を受けた。\r\nその後――",
            "enText": "As a trainer, I was interviewed for the \nschool newspaper. Afterwards—",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "pathId": -2342852445894630012,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと、こちらをじっと見ている\r\nメジロドーベルに気づいた。",
            "enText": "Suddenly I noticed a white-tailed \ndobel staring at me.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "pathId": -1874947171766384198,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "あんなに撮られたのに、すごい自然体……。\r\nアタシも……ああなれたら……。",
            "enText": "Even though she was photographed \nso much, she looked so natural… \nI wish I could be… like that.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どうかした？",
                    "enText": "What's wrong?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2513610215164161363,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "っ……べ、別に。なんでもない。",
            "enText": "… Nothing. It's nothing.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "pathId": 1664572321636128214,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "へ！？　あ、えっと……！",
            "enText": "Heh! Uh, let's see…!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "pathId": 8053046218893477157,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……アンタには関係ない。\r\n……アタシの問題だから。",
            "enText": "…It's not your problem. It's… my problem.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "pathId": 4284195353287419458,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと、こちらを見ていた時に、\r\n『アタシも……ああなれたら……』と\nこぼしていたことを思い出した。",
            "enText": "I suddenly remembered that when I was \nlooking at you, I had spilled the words \"I \nwish I could… be like…\".",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……写真が苦手なのか？",
                    "enText": "… Not good at photography?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1775479706291715604,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……っえ、なんで……。",
            "enText": "… Eh, why not…",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "pathId": 448957281851928367,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "どうやら本当に写真が苦手らしい。\r\n何か力になれればと思い、\nアドバイスを送ることにした。",
            "enText": "Apparently, I'm really bad at photography. \nI thought I'd send her some advice \nto see if I could help.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "体を鍛えて自信をつけよう！",
                    "enText": "Build your body, build your confidence!",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "鏡の前で笑顔の練習！",
                    "enText": "Practise your smile in front of the mirror!",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3474084352505256114,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "も、もしよかったら……\r\n写真に上手く写るコツ、教えてもらえない？",
            "enText": "If you'd like to learn more about how to get \nthe best out of… please let me know.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "写真が苦手なの？",
                    "enText": "Not good at photography?",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3193607952110205288,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……アタシ、注目されるのが苦手で、\r\n取材とかでも、いつも上手く笑えないの。",
            "enText": "… I don't like to be the centre of \nattention and I don't always smile \nwell when I do interviews.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "pathId": -4300703031777820885,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "でも本当はちゃんと、\r\n堂々とした笑顔で写りたくて……。",
            "enText": "But the truth is, I wanted to be \nphotographed with a proper, regal smile…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "体を鍛えて自信をつけよう！",
                    "enText": "Build your body, build your confidence!",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "鏡の前で笑顔の練習！",
                    "enText": "Practise your smile in front of the mirror!",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6053915942199371592,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……別に、聞いてないんだけど。",
            "enText": "… Apart from that, I'm not asking.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "pathId": 8622832132378003451,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "自信、か……。",
            "enText": "Confidence, or…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "pathId": -6173684258192685557,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "そっか。もう少し自信が持てたら、\r\n自然に笑えるのかな。",
            "enText": "I see. If I had more confidence, I would be \nable to laugh naturally.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "pathId": 5989020726147628272,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……うん。体力づくりも兼ねてやってみる。\r\nありがとう。",
            "enText": "… Yeah. I'm going to try it for \nfitness as well. Thank you.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": -776468757412648410,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう言って彼女は立ち去ってしまった。",
            "enText": "And with that, she walked away.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "pathId": -4558863795946776159,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……自信が持てたら、\r\n自然に笑えるのかな。",
            "enText": "… I wonder if I could laugh naturally \nif I had more confidence.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "pathId": 7292225499767071229,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……気が向いたらやってみよう。",
            "enText": "… I'll give it a go if I feel like it.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": -2654090178795717456,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "鏡って……なにそれ、変なの。",
            "enText": "A mirror is… what it is, weird.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "pathId": 2202518276585765165,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "鏡の前で笑顔……か。\r\nちょっと恥ずかしいな。",
            "enText": "You smile in front of the mirror…? \nThat's a bit embarrassing.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "pathId": 7389665364591622275,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……まあ……。",
            "enText": "… well…",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "pathId": 3032028436794863895,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "その……、覚えとく。",
            "enText": "I'll remember that…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": -6897688071214991759,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "……でも、手軽にできるし、\r\n自分の姿がわかるのはいいかも。",
            "enText": "It's easy to do on… and it's good \nto see what you look like.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "pathId": -3880239597053543020,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロドーベル",
            "enName": "Mejiro Dober",
            "jpText": "ありがとう。\r\nちょっと、やってみる。",
            "enText": "Thank you. I'll give it a go.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": 1588962259214025085,
            "blockIdx": 25
        }
    ]
}